## [Secrets & Sensitive Configuration]
# Exclude appsettings files that contain secrets (connection strings, API keys, etc.)
# Keep appsettings.Development.json as a template/reference only if needed
**/appsettings.json
**/appsettings.Production.json
# Allow example/template files to be committed
!**/appsettings.Example.json
